HEADWORD: Scirrhous
<hw>Scir"rhous</hw> <pr>(sk⟦icr⟧r"r⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>scirrhosus</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Proceeding from
